What is the output of the following C program fragment?
int a = 1;
int b = 1;
int c = ++a || b++;
int d = b-- && --a;

printf("%d %d %d %d", d, c, b, a);

a) 1111
b) 0100
c) 1001
d) 1101

Remember the short circuiting when a condition is met.
TRUE || anything == TRUE
